                                 <p>Vellum, about 7 7/8 in. by 5 1/8, consisting of 115 leaves, the
                                    first of which, being blank, is not numbered. A few of them are
                                    slightly stained and soiled. The quires, signed with letters,
                                    are 12 in number. There are from 23 to 33 lines in each
                                    page.</p>
